headline: Principal Financial (PFG) Stock Outlook Adjusted by JPMorgan Amid Life Insurance Peer Comparison
summary: Principal Financial Group (NASDAQ:PFG) ranks among the biggest publicly traded asset managers. JPMorgan dropped Principal Financial Group (NASDAQ:PFG) from Overweight to Neutral on January 5, with a $103 price target. The firm clarified that the adjustment represents “better perceived value in other life insurance stocks” instead of an actual change in Principal Financial Group’s outlook. […]
